Put biting insects in goblin tents ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

The old Dwarf-hold of Sundergrót lays in partial ruins next to the Floodfells. Its halls are crawling with various insects from the depths. Perhaps you could find some of the more nibbling variety and give them as a gift to those goblins sleeping in the old dwarf structure. It just might shorten the goblins' stay!
Sundergrót can be found in the Floodfells.\n\nYou should seek out goblin tents in Sundergrót.
